These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, photography, dancing, hiking, baking, gardening, traveling
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is baking is the dutch##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 4. the british is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the german##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking | woodworking | photography | traveling  | gardening  | hiking    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

